@startuml architecture
' 系统总体架构图
' 生成方式：IDEA 装PlantUML插件 → 打开此文件 → 右键 Preview → 导出PNG

title 榫卯非遗文化传承平台 - 系统总体架构图

skinparam rectangle {
    BackgroundColor #F5F5F5
    BorderColor #666666
}

rectangle "前端 (微信小程序原生)" as Frontend {
    rectangle "pages/\n(27个页面)" as Pages
    rectangle "custom-tab-bar\n(5项底部导航)" as TabBar
    rectangle "app.js\n(全局逻辑+请求封装)" as AppJs
}

rectangle "后端 (Spring Boot 2.7.18)" as Backend {
    rectangle "Controller 层\n(18个控制器)" as Ctrl
    rectangle "Service 层\n(15个服务)" as Svc
    rectangle "Mapper 层\n(MyBatis-Plus)" as Mapper
    rectangle "Entity 层\n(16个实体)" as Entity
}

rectangle "数据层" as Data {
    database "MySQL 8.0\nljx_platform库\n(17张表)" as DB
    rectangle "本地 uploads/\n(图片存储)" as Disk
}

rectangle "第三方服务" as Third {
    rectangle "DeepSeek API\n(AI文化导师)" as AI
}

Frontend --> Ctrl : HTTP/JSON (wx.request)
Ctrl --> Svc
Svc --> Mapper
Mapper --> Entity
Mapper --> DB : JDBC (Druid连接池)
Ctrl --> Disk : FileSystemResource\n(静态资源访问)
Svc --> AI : HTTP POST\napi.deepseek.com

@enduml
